source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000010_GILGAMESH<tab>To my side, Enkidu! The battle is joined!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000010_GILGAMESH<tab>Allez, on y va, Enkidu, mon vieil ami<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000020_GILGAMESH<tab>Owww! It hurts! It hurts!Enkidu! Your master wants for succor!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000020_GILGAMESH<tab>C'est qu'ils n'y vont pas de main morte<var 1D /var>!<var 1D /var>... Enkidu, soigne-moi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000030_GILGAMESH<tab>Fancy some feathers...bird brain?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000030_GILGAMESH<tab>Par ici, mes petits poulets<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000040_GILGAMESH<tab>This should cut you down to size...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000040_GILGAMESH<tab>Retournez jouer à la poupée<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000050_GILGAMESH<tab>Fight on, Enkidu, my ever faithful─hm!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000050_GILGAMESH<tab>Enkidu<var 1D /var>! Prends la relève<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000060_GILGAMESH<tab>Enkidu! Are the bonds of our friendship so fragile!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000060_GILGAMESH<tab>Enkidu<var 1D /var>!? Tu ne vas pas me lâcher maintenant<var 1D /var>!?

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000070_GILGAMESH<tab>Not the <var 1A 02 /var>strongest<var 1A 01 /var> of swords, but it should suffice.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000070_GILGAMESH<tab>Goûtez au tranchant de Masamune<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000080_GILGAMESH<tab>Gilgamesh is in the mood...for dancing!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000080_GILGAMESH<tab>Et maintenant, la danse du sabre<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000090_GILGAMESH<tab>Divide and conquer, Gilgamesh style!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000090_GILGAMESH<tab>Admirez la beauté mortelle de Neige, Lune et Fleurs<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000100_GILGAMESH<tab>...And now for something truly <var 1A 02 /var>shocking<var 1A 01 /var>!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000100_GILGAMESH<tab>On dirait bien que vous avez le coup de foudre<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000110_GILGAMESH<tab>What's the matter, friend? All tied up?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000110_GILGAMESH<tab>Et hop, un joli coup de filet<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000120_GILGAMESH<tab>Uh-oh! Someone just woke the dragon...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000120_GILGAMESH<tab>Prenez ça... Fléau du dragon<var 1D /var>!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000130_GILGAMESH<tab>You have some skill, I'll give you that...
But Gilgamesh has only just begun to fight!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000130_GILGAMESH<tab>Pas mal<var 1D /var>! Pas mal<var 1D /var>! Mais le combat ne fait que commencer<var 1D /var>!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000140_GILGAMESH<tab>Most impressive!
Very well─I, too, shall fight with all my strength!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000140_GILGAMESH<tab>Raaah<var 1D /var>! C'est moins facile que prévu... Allez, pas de quartier<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000150_GILGAMESH<tab>No! The mighty Gilgamesh will not be defeated!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_000150_GILGAMESH<tab>Je... je n'ai pas dit mon dernier mot<var 1D /var>!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_100010_GILGAMESH<tab>At long last, we meet again on the battlefield!
I daresay Enkidu shall come to enjoy our tussles as much as I.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_100010_GILGAMESH<tab><var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>, je suis tellement heureux de pouvoir vous affronter à nouveau<var 1D /var>!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_100020_GILGAMESH<tab><var 1A 02 /var>You<var 1A 01 /var>, however, might not find this one so enjoyable.
...Unless you enjoy getting pounded senseless. Hah!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_100020_GILGAMESH<tab>Je crois que ce vieux château en ruine est l'endroit idéal pour une revanche. Enkidu et moi, nous allons vous montrer de quoi nous sommes capables<var 1D /var>!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200010_GILGAMESH<tab><var 1A 02 /var>Me<var 1A 01 /var>? Run away? Hah! I-I was but seeking out a
more suitable spot to celebrate my inevitable victory!
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200010_GILGAMESH<tab>Mouahahaha<var 1D /var>! Vous croyiez peut-être que j'allais m'échapper<var 1D /var>!?
Non, Gilgamesh ne fuit jamais devant un adversaire<var 1D /var>! C'est pour vous infliger le coup de grâce que je suis venu ici<var 1D /var>!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200020_GILGAMESH<tab>But enough exposition! Now we fight like men!
And ladies! And ladies who dress like men!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200020_GILGAMESH<tab>Vous allez voir de quoi je suis vraiment capable<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200030_GILGAMESH<tab>For Gilgamesh...it is transmogrifying time!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200030_GILGAMESH<tab>Tremblez devant le VRAI Gilgamesh<var 1D /var>!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200040_GILGAMESH<tab>The mightiest warrior ever to grace Eorzea stands before you─
by which I mean <var 1A 02 /var>I<var 1A 01 /var>, Gilgamesh! Prepare yourself!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_200040_GILGAMESH<tab>Il n'est de plus puissant bretteur que moi<var 1D /var>! Vous allez en avoir la preuve<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300010_GILGAMESH<tab>To think that my full complement of arms would avail me naught...
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300010_GILGAMESH<tab>Incroyable<var 1D /var>! Même avec quatre paires de bras, je n'arrive pas à vous battre<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300020_GILGAMESH<tab>No more high jinks from Gilgamesh. You have my word.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300020_GILGAMESH<tab>Je... je suis désolé... Je vous promets que je ne ferai plus rien de mal.

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300030_GILGAMESH<tab>The Treaty-Blade, too, I shall return.
...Just as soon as I remember where I hid it.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300030_GILGAMESH<tab>Pour vous le prouver, je vais vous rendre l'Épée du Pacte. Elle est cachée dans la forêt, près d'ici.

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300040_GILGAMESH<tab>Anyway, I yield to your unparalleled puissance!
Spare my insignificant life, I beg of you!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_300040_GILGAMESH<tab>Je vous en supplie<var 1D /var>! Pardonnez-moi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400010_GILGAMESH<tab>...NOT! Ha, I lied...again! Like a rug! Oh, I kill me!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400010_GILGAMESH<tab>Ils ne croyaient quand même pas que cette vieille relique m'intéressait<var 1D /var>!?

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400020_GILGAMESH<tab>You can take that fusty old blade for all I care! I thirst for <var 1A 02 /var>true<var 1A 01 /var>
power, and naught save the strongest of swords will suffice!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400020_GILGAMESH<tab>Moi, ce que je veux, ce sont les armes les plus puissantes d'Éorzéa<var 1D /var>!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400030_GILGAMESH<tab>Warrior of Light─you have proven a worthy opponent.
But I warn you─treasure every moment with your weapon.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400030_GILGAMESH<tab>Je dois dire que ce<var 08 E905 ((tte Guerrière)) (( Guerrier)) /var> de la Lumière est vraiment un adversaire redoutable... Mais la prochaine fois, c'est moi qui gagnerai<var 1D /var>! Foi de Gilgamesh<var 1D /var>!

source:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400040_GILGAMESH<tab>For as sure as day follows night, the hour will come when
I claim it as mine own! Till we meet again!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03000_400040_GILGAMESH<tab>Et toutes leurs armes seront à moi<var 1D /var>! On se reverra bientôt<var 1D /var>!
